Emily, Sarah, Iris,

792
01:22:57,522 --> 01:23:00,275
Kristen...

793
01:23:00,275 --> 01:23:03,394
You can forget all about them now.

794
01:23:05,280 --> 01:23:08,950
When can I get out of here?
I really just wanna go home.

795
